<MethodEndpoint

  context={"endpoint"}
>
  
</MethodEndpoint>



Returns a list of your domain applications. The domain applications
are returned sorted by creation date, with the most recent domain
applications appearing first. The list is filterable by sending in any
of the following parameters.

#### Permissions
The API token must include the following scopes: _Voice_.
